headline: Is the Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF a Buy Now?
summary: Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF uses a complex screening approach.  The ETF's screens are likely to be very similar to the screens you would use to pick dividend stocks individually.  Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF has a fairly attractive 4% yield.
